text: Eunidia cyanoptera is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1910. It contains the variety Eunidia cyanoptera var. nigripes.BioLib.cz - Eunidia cyanoptera. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1910
